def_cn: （系统、机构等）负担过重的，不堪重负的
def_en: If a system or organization is overburdened, it has too many people or things to deal with and so does not function properly.

def_cn: （人因工作、问题等）负担过重的，不堪应付的
def_en: If you are overburdened with something such as work or problems, you have more of it than you can cope with.
